            "text": "From the first glance, this C3 Corvette sure makes a lasting impression. The optional two-tone White and Silver exterior has been shined to near perfection. All factory badging and trim appears to be present and in excellent condition. Even the upgraded OE aluminum wheels glisten in the sunlight. A lack of cosmetic damage allows the long hood a and that T-top roof to really captivate your eye.",
