          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Other factory options have been added to this ‘Vette for a more luxuriously-appointed Light Gray interior. It all starts with leather seats. An AM/FM cassette stereo means you can rock out like old times. Thanks to a power driver’s seat, tilt/telescoping steering column, and power mirrors you can find the ideal position for driving this American classic.",
